reviewText: I absolutely love this movie! I owned a copy before but never came back after I borrowed it off to someone, so having this in my hands again felt complete!! It shipped pretty quickly and after I received it, I watched it three more times with my friends :)
Came in a lot faster than it was suppose to. Love love. The only thing is the cd holder case it came in, was cracked. The DVD itself is fine. But eh. I love this movie. Its a great chinese classic.
